{"key":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01|Gal|1","bibleId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01","bookAbbr":"Gal","chapter":1,"textRevision":"api-bible-csb-2024","parserRevision":"v10","verses":[{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Gal:1:1","bibleId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01","bookAbbr":"Gal","bookOrder":47,"chapter":1,"verse":1,"text":"Paul, an apostle —not from men or by man, but by Jesus Christ and God the Father who raised him from the dead —","textRevision":"api-bible-csb-2024"},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Gal:1:2","bibleId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01","bookAbbr":"Gal","bookOrder":47,"chapter":1,"verse":2,"text":"and all the brothers who are with me:","textRevision":"api-bible-csb-2024"},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Gal:1:3","bibleId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01","bookAbbr":"Gal","bookOrder":47,"chapter":1,"verse":3,"text":"Grace to you and peace from God the Father and our Lord Jesus Christ,","textRevision":"api-bible-csb-2024"},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Gal:1:4","bibleId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01","bookAbbr":"Gal","bookOrder":47,"chapter":1,"verse":4,"text":"who gave himself for our sins to rescue us from this present evil age, according to the will of our God and Father.","textRevision":"api-bible-csb-2024"},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Gal:1:5","bibleId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01","bookAbbr":"Gal","bookOrder":47,"chapter":1,"verse":5,"text":"To him be the glory forever and ever. Amen.","textRevision":"api-bible-csb-2024"},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Gal:1:6","bibleId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01","bookAbbr":"Gal","bookOrder":47,"chapter":1,"verse":6,"text":"I am amazed that you are so quickly turning away from him who called you by the grace of Christ and are turning to a different gospel —","textRevision":"api-bible-csb-2024"},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Gal:1:7","bibleId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01","bookAbbr":"Gal","bookOrder":47,"chapter":1,"verse":7,"text":"not that there is another gospel, but there are some who are troubling you and want to distort the gospel of Christ.","textRevision":"api-bible-csb-2024"},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Gal:1:8","bibleId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01","bookAbbr":"Gal","bookOrder":47,"chapter":1,"verse":8,"text":"But even if we or an angel from heaven should preach to you a gospel contrary to what we have preached to you, a curse be on him!","textRevision":"api-bible-csb-2024"},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Gal:1:9","bibleId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01","bookAbbr":"Gal","bookOrder":47,"chapter":1,"verse":9,"text":"As we have said before, I now say again: If anyone is preaching to you a gospel contrary to what you received, a curse be on him!","textRevision":"api-bible-csb-2024"},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Gal:1:10","bibleId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01","bookAbbr":"Gal","bookOrder":47,"chapter":1,"verse":10,"text":"For am I now trying to persuade people, or God? Or am I striving to please people? If I were still trying to please people, I would not be a servant of Christ.","textRevision":"api-bible-csb-2024"},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Gal:1:11","bibleId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01","bookAbbr":"Gal","bookOrder":47,"chapter":1,"verse":11,"text":"For I want you to know, brothers and sisters, that the gospel preached by me is not of human origin.","textRevision":"api-bible-csb-2024"},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Gal:1:12","bibleId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01","bookAbbr":"Gal","bookOrder":47,"chapter":1,"verse":12,"text":"For I did not receive it from a human source and I was not taught it, but it came by a revelation of Jesus Christ.","textRevision":"api-bible-csb-2024"},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Gal:1:13","bibleId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01","bookAbbr":"Gal","bookOrder":47,"chapter":1,"verse":13,"text":"For you have heard about my former way of life in Judaism: I intensely persecuted God’s church and tried to destroy it.","textRevision":"api-bible-csb-2024"},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Gal:1:14","bibleId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01","bookAbbr":"Gal","bookOrder":47,"chapter":1,"verse":14,"text":"I advanced in Judaism beyond many contemporaries among my people, because I was extremely zealous for the traditions of my ancestors.","textRevision":"api-bible-csb-2024"},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Gal:1:15","bibleId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01","bookAbbr":"Gal","bookOrder":47,"chapter":1,"verse":15,"text":"But when God, who from my mother’s womb set me apart and called me by his grace, was pleased","textRevision":"api-bible-csb-2024"},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Gal:1:16","bibleId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01","bookAbbr":"Gal","bookOrder":47,"chapter":1,"verse":16,"text":"to reveal his Son in me, so that I could preach him among the Gentiles, I did not immediately consult with anyone.","textRevision":"api-bible-csb-2024"},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Gal:1:17","bibleId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01","bookAbbr":"Gal","bookOrder":47,"chapter":1,"verse":17,"text":"I did not go up to Jerusalem to those who had become apostles before me; instead I went to Arabia and came back to Damascus.","textRevision":"api-bible-csb-2024"},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Gal:1:18","bibleId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01","bookAbbr":"Gal","bookOrder":47,"chapter":1,"verse":18,"text":"Then after three years I did go up to Jerusalem to get to know Cephas, and I stayed with him fifteen days.","textRevision":"api-bible-csb-2024"},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Gal:1:19","bibleId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01","bookAbbr":"Gal","bookOrder":47,"chapter":1,"verse":19,"text":"But I didn’t see any of the other apostles except James, the Lord’s brother.","textRevision":"api-bible-csb-2024"},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Gal:1:20","bibleId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01","bookAbbr":"Gal","bookOrder":47,"chapter":1,"verse":20,"text":"I declare in the sight of God: I am not lying in what I write to you.","textRevision":"api-bible-csb-2024"},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Gal:1:21","bibleId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01","bookAbbr":"Gal","bookOrder":47,"chapter":1,"verse":21,"text":"Afterward, I went to the regions of Syria and Cilicia.","textRevision":"api-bible-csb-2024"},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Gal:1:22","bibleId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01","bookAbbr":"Gal","bookOrder":47,"chapter":1,"verse":22,"text":"I remained personally unknown to the Judean churches that are in Christ.","textRevision":"api-bible-csb-2024"},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Gal:1:23","bibleId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01","bookAbbr":"Gal","bookOrder":47,"chapter":1,"verse":23,"text":"They simply kept hearing, “He who formerly persecuted us now preaches the faith he once tried to destroy.”","textRevision":"api-bible-csb-2024"},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Gal:1:24","bibleId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01","bookAbbr":"Gal","bookOrder":47,"chapter":1,"verse":24,"text":"And they glorified God because of me.","textRevision":"api-bible-csb-2024"}],"layout":{"bibleId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01","bookAbbr":"Gal","chapter":1,"paragraphStarts":[1,3,6,10,11,13,18,21],"headings":[{"beforeVerse":1,"text":"Greeting"},{"beforeVerse":6,"text":"No Other Gospel"},{"beforeVerse":11,"text":"The Origin of Paul’s Gospel"}],"poetryBlocks":[],"studyByVerse":[{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Gal:1:1","parts":[{"kind":"text","text":"Paul, "},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Ac 13:9","book":"Act","chapter":13,"verse":9,"letter":"a"},{"kind":"text","text":" an apostle —not from men or by man, but by Jesus Christ and God the Father "},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Mt 5:16","book":"Mat","chapter":5,"verse":16,"letter":"b"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Mt 6:1","book":"Mat","chapter":6,"verse":1,"letter":"c"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Mt 11:27","book":"Mat","chapter":11,"verse":27,"letter":"d"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Jn 8:42","book":"Jhn","chapter":8,"verse":42,"letter":"e"},{"kind":"text","text":" who raised him from the dead "},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Ac 9:6","book":"Act","chapter":9,"verse":6,"letter":"f"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Ac 20:24","book":"Act","chapter":20,"verse":24,"letter":"g"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Ac 22:10–21","book":"Act","chapter":22,"verse":10,"letter":"h"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Ac 26:16","book":"Act","chapter":26,"verse":16,"letter":"i"},{"kind":"text","text":" — "}],"crossRefs":[{"label":"Ac 13:9","book":"Act","chapter":13,"verse":9},{"label":"Mt 5:16","book":"Mat","chapter":5,"verse":16},{"label":"Mt 6:1","book":"Mat","chapter":6,"verse":1},{"label":"Mt 11:27","book":"Mat","chapter":11,"verse":27},{"label":"Jn 8:42","book":"Jhn","chapter":8,"verse":42},{"label":"Ac 9:6","book":"Act","chapter":9,"verse":6},{"label":"Ac 20:24","book":"Act","chapter":20,"verse":24},{"label":"Ac 22:10–21","book":"Act","chapter":22,"verse":10},{"label":"Ac 26:16","book":"Act","chapter":26,"verse":16}],"footnotes":[]},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Gal:1:2","parts":[{"kind":"text","text":"and all the brothers who are with me:"}],"crossRefs":[],"footnotes":[]},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Gal:1:3","parts":[{"kind":"text","text":"Grace to you and peace from God the Father and our Lord "},{"kind":"footnote","marker":1,"text":"Other mss read God our Father and the Lord"},{"kind":"text","text":" Jesus Christ, "}],"crossRefs":[],"footnotes":[{"marker":1,"text":"Other mss read God our Father and the Lord"}]},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Gal:1:4","parts":[{"kind":"text","text":"who gave himself for our sins "},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Rm 6:23","book":"Rom","chapter":6,"verse":23,"letter":"a"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Ti 2:14","book":"Tit","chapter":2,"verse":14,"letter":"b"},{"kind":"text","text":" to rescue us from this present evil age, "},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Mt 20:28","book":"Mat","chapter":20,"verse":28,"letter":"c"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Rm 4:25","book":"Rom","chapter":4,"verse":25,"letter":"d"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"1Co 15:3","book":"1Co","chapter":15,"verse":3,"letter":"e"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Gl 2:20","book":"Gal","chapter":2,"verse":20,"letter":"f"},{"kind":"text","text":" according to the will of our God and Father. "},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Php 4:20","book":"Php","chapter":4,"verse":20,"letter":"g"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"1Th 1:3","book":"1Th","chapter":1,"verse":3,"letter":"h"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"1Th 3:11","book":"1Th","chapter":3,"verse":11,"letter":"i"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"1Th 3:13","book":"1Th","chapter":3,"verse":13,"letter":"j"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Heb 10:7","book":"Heb","chapter":10,"verse":7,"letter":"k"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"1Pt 3:17","book":"1Pe","chapter":3,"verse":17,"letter":"l"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Rv 10:7","book":"Rev","chapter":10,"verse":7,"letter":"m"},{"kind":"text","text":" "}],"crossRefs":[{"label":"Rm 6:23","book":"Rom","chapter":6,"verse":23},{"label":"Ti 2:14","book":"Tit","chapter":2,"verse":14},{"label":"Mt 20:28","book":"Mat","chapter":20,"verse":28},{"label":"Rm 4:25","book":"Rom","chapter":4,"verse":25},{"label":"1Co 15:3","book":"1Co","chapter":15,"verse":3},{"label":"Gl 2:20","book":"Gal","chapter":2,"verse":20},{"label":"Php 4:20","book":"Php","chapter":4,"verse":20},{"label":"1Th 1:3","book":"1Th","chapter":1,"verse":3},{"label":"1Th 3:11","book":"1Th","chapter":3,"verse":11},{"label":"1Th 3:13","book":"1Th","chapter":3,"verse":13},{"label":"Heb 10:7","book":"Heb","chapter":10,"verse":7},{"label":"1Pt 3:17","book":"1Pe","chapter":3,"verse":17},{"label":"Rv 10:7","book":"Rev","chapter":10,"verse":7}],"footnotes":[]},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Gal:1:5","parts":[{"kind":"text","text":"To him be the glory forever and ever. Amen."}],"crossRefs":[],"footnotes":[]},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Gal:1:6","parts":[{"kind":"text","text":"I am amazed that you are so quickly turning away from him who called "},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Col 3:15","book":"Col","chapter":3,"verse":15,"letter":"a"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"1Pt 1:15","book":"1Pe","chapter":1,"verse":15,"letter":"b"},{"kind":"text","text":" you by the grace of Christ and are turning to a different gospel — "}],"crossRefs":[{"label":"Col 3:15","book":"Col","chapter":3,"verse":15},{"label":"1Pt 1:15","book":"1Pe","chapter":1,"verse":15}],"footnotes":[]},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Gal:1:7","parts":[{"kind":"text","text":"not that there is another gospel, "},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Ac 4:12","book":"Act","chapter":4,"verse":12,"letter":"a"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"1Co 3:11","book":"1Co","chapter":3,"verse":11,"letter":"b"},{"kind":"text","text":" but there are some "},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Jd 1:4","book":"Jud","chapter":1,"verse":4,"letter":"c"},{"kind":"text","text":" who are troubling you and want to distort the gospel of Christ. "}],"crossRefs":[{"label":"Ac 4:12","book":"Act","chapter":4,"verse":12},{"label":"1Co 3:11","book":"1Co","chapter":3,"verse":11},{"label":"Jd 1:4","book":"Jud","chapter":1,"verse":4}],"footnotes":[]},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Gal:1:8","parts":[{"kind":"text","text":"But even if we or an angel "},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Gn 16:7","book":"Gen","chapter":16,"verse":7,"letter":"a"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Mt 13:49","book":"Mat","chapter":13,"verse":49,"letter":"b"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Lk 1:11","book":"Luk","chapter":1,"verse":11,"letter":"c"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Ac 5:19","book":"Act","chapter":5,"verse":19,"letter":"d"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Rv 14:6","book":"Rev","chapter":14,"verse":6,"letter":"e"},{"kind":"text","text":" from heaven should preach to you a gospel contrary to what we have preached to you, "},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Rm 15:20","book":"Rom","chapter":15,"verse":20,"letter":"f"},{"kind":"text","text":" a curse be on him! "},{"kind":"footnote","marker":1,"text":"Or you, let him be condemned, or you, let him be condemned to hell; Gk anathema"},{"kind":"text","text":" "}],"crossRefs":[{"label":"Gn 16:7","book":"Gen","chapter":16,"verse":7},{"label":"Mt 13:49","book":"Mat","chapter":13,"verse":49},{"label":"Lk 1:11","book":"Luk","chapter":1,"verse":11},{"label":"Ac 5:19","book":"Act","chapter":5,"verse":19},{"label":"Rv 14:6","book":"Rev","chapter":14,"verse":6},{"label":"Rm 15:20","book":"Rom","chapter":15,"verse":20}],"footnotes":[{"marker":1,"text":"Or you, let him be condemned, or you, let him be condemned to hell; Gk anathema"}]},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Gal:1:9","parts":[{"kind":"text","text":"As we have said before, I now say again: If anyone is preaching to you a gospel contrary to what you received, "},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Jd 1:3","book":"Jud","chapter":1,"verse":3,"letter":"a"},{"kind":"text","text":" a curse be on him!"}],"crossRefs":[{"label":"Jd 1:3","book":"Jud","chapter":1,"verse":3}],"footnotes":[]},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Gal:1:10","parts":[{"kind":"text","text":"For am I now trying to persuade people, "},{"kind":"footnote","marker":1,"text":"Or win the approval of people"},{"kind":"text","text":" or God? "},{"kind":"crossref","label":"1Th 2:4","book":"1Th","chapter":2,"verse":4,"letter":"a"},{"kind":"text","text":" Or am I striving to please people? If I were still trying to please people, I would not be a servant of Christ."}],"crossRefs":[{"label":"1Th 2:4","book":"1Th","chapter":2,"verse":4}],"footnotes":[{"marker":1,"text":"Or win the approval of people"}]},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Gal:1:11","parts":[{"kind":"text","text":"For I want you to know, brothers and sisters, that the gospel preached by me is not of human origin. "}],"crossRefs":[],"footnotes":[]},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Gal:1:12","parts":[{"kind":"text","text":"For I did not receive it from a human source and I was not taught it, but it came by a revelation "},{"kind":"crossref","label":"1Pt 4:13","book":"1Pe","chapter":4,"verse":13,"letter":"a"},{"kind":"text","text":" of Jesus Christ. "},{"kind":"crossref","label":"1Co 11:23","book":"1Co","chapter":11,"verse":23,"letter":"b"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"1Co 15:3","book":"1Co","chapter":15,"verse":3,"letter":"c"}],"crossRefs":[{"label":"1Pt 4:13","book":"1Pe","chapter":4,"verse":13},{"label":"1Co 11:23","book":"1Co","chapter":11,"verse":23},{"label":"1Co 15:3","book":"1Co","chapter":15,"verse":3}],"footnotes":[]},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Gal:1:13","parts":[{"kind":"text","text":"For you have heard about my former way of life "},{"kind":"crossref","label":"2Pt 3:11","book":"2Pe","chapter":3,"verse":11,"letter":"a"},{"kind":"text","text":" in Judaism: "},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Ac 8:1","book":"Act","chapter":8,"verse":1,"letter":"b"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Ac 26:4","book":"Act","chapter":26,"verse":4,"letter":"c"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Php 3:5–6","book":"Php","chapter":3,"verse":5,"letter":"d"},{"kind":"text","text":" I intensely persecuted "},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Php 3:6","book":"Php","chapter":3,"verse":6,"letter":"e"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"2Tm 3:12","book":"2Ti","chapter":3,"verse":12,"letter":"f"},{"kind":"text","text":" God’s church and tried to destroy it. "}],"crossRefs":[{"label":"2Pt 3:11","book":"2Pe","chapter":3,"verse":11},{"label":"Ac 8:1","book":"Act","chapter":8,"verse":1},{"label":"Ac 26:4","book":"Act","chapter":26,"verse":4},{"label":"Php 3:5–6","book":"Php","chapter":3,"verse":5},{"label":"Php 3:6","book":"Php","chapter":3,"verse":6},{"label":"2Tm 3:12","book":"2Ti","chapter":3,"verse":12}],"footnotes":[]},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Gal:1:14","parts":[{"kind":"text","text":"I advanced in Judaism beyond many contemporaries among my people, because I was extremely zealous for the traditions of my ancestors. "},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Mk 7:3","book":"Mrk","chapter":7,"verse":3,"letter":"a"},{"kind":"text","text":" "}],"crossRefs":[{"label":"Mk 7:3","book":"Mrk","chapter":7,"verse":3}],"footnotes":[]},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Gal:1:15","parts":[{"kind":"text","text":"But when God, who from my mother’s womb set me apart and called "},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Mt 24:22","book":"Mat","chapter":24,"verse":22,"letter":"a"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Col 3:15","book":"Col","chapter":3,"verse":15,"letter":"b"},{"kind":"text","text":" me by his grace, was pleased "}],"crossRefs":[{"label":"Mt 24:22","book":"Mat","chapter":24,"verse":22},{"label":"Col 3:15","book":"Col","chapter":3,"verse":15}],"footnotes":[]},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Gal:1:16","parts":[{"kind":"text","text":"to reveal his Son "},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Jn 5:19","book":"Jhn","chapter":5,"verse":19,"letter":"a"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Heb 1:2","book":"Heb","chapter":1,"verse":2,"letter":"b"},{"kind":"text","text":" in me, so that I could preach him among the Gentiles, I did not immediately consult with anyone. "},{"kind":"footnote","marker":1,"text":"Lit flesh and blood"},{"kind":"text","text":" "}],"crossRefs":[{"label":"Jn 5:19","book":"Jhn","chapter":5,"verse":19},{"label":"Heb 1:2","book":"Heb","chapter":1,"verse":2}],"footnotes":[{"marker":1,"text":"Lit flesh and blood"}]},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Gal:1:17","parts":[{"kind":"text","text":"I did not go up to Jerusalem "},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Mt 23:37","book":"Mat","chapter":23,"verse":37,"letter":"a"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Ac 8:1","book":"Act","chapter":8,"verse":1,"letter":"b"},{"kind":"text","text":" to those who had become apostles "},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Jd 1:17","book":"Jud","chapter":1,"verse":17,"letter":"c"},{"kind":"text","text":" before me; instead I went to Arabia "},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Is 21:13","book":"Isa","chapter":21,"verse":13,"letter":"d"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Jr 25:24","book":"Jer","chapter":25,"verse":24,"letter":"e"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Ezk 27:21","book":"Ezk","chapter":27,"verse":21,"letter":"f"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Gl 4:25","book":"Gal","chapter":4,"verse":25,"letter":"g"},{"kind":"text","text":" and came back to Damascus. "},{"kind":"crossref","label":"2Sm 8:5","book":"2Sa","chapter":8,"verse":5,"letter":"h"}],"crossRefs":[{"label":"Mt 23:37","book":"Mat","chapter":23,"verse":37},{"label":"Ac 8:1","book":"Act","chapter":8,"verse":1},{"label":"Jd 1:17","book":"Jud","chapter":1,"verse":17},{"label":"Is 21:13","book":"Isa","chapter":21,"verse":13},{"label":"Jr 25:24","book":"Jer","chapter":25,"verse":24},{"label":"Ezk 27:21","book":"Ezk","chapter":27,"verse":21},{"label":"Gl 4:25","book":"Gal","chapter":4,"verse":25},{"label":"2Sm 8:5","book":"2Sa","chapter":8,"verse":5}],"footnotes":[]},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Gal:1:18","parts":[{"kind":"text","text":"Then after three years I did go up to Jerusalem "},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Ac 9:26","book":"Act","chapter":9,"verse":26,"letter":"a"},{"kind":"text","text":" to get to know Cephas, "},{"kind":"footnote","marker":1,"text":"Other mss read Peter"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Jn 1:42","book":"Jhn","chapter":1,"verse":42,"letter":"b"},{"kind":"text","text":" and I stayed with him fifteen days. "}],"crossRefs":[{"label":"Ac 9:26","book":"Act","chapter":9,"verse":26},{"label":"Jn 1:42","book":"Jhn","chapter":1,"verse":42}],"footnotes":[{"marker":1,"text":"Other mss read Peter"}]},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Gal:1:19","parts":[{"kind":"text","text":"But I didn’t see any of the other apostles except James, "},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Jd 1:1","book":"Jud","chapter":1,"verse":1,"letter":"a"},{"kind":"text","text":" the Lord’s brother. "}],"crossRefs":[{"label":"Jd 1:1","book":"Jud","chapter":1,"verse":1}],"footnotes":[]},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Gal:1:20","parts":[{"kind":"text","text":"I declare in the sight of God: I am not lying in what I write to you."}],"crossRefs":[],"footnotes":[]},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Gal:1:21","parts":[{"kind":"text","text":"Afterward, I went to the regions of Syria "},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Nm 23:7","book":"Num","chapter":23,"verse":7,"letter":"a"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Lk 2:2","book":"Luk","chapter":2,"verse":2,"letter":"b"},{"kind":"text","text":" and Cilicia. "},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Ac 9:30","book":"Act","chapter":9,"verse":30,"letter":"c"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Ac 11:25–26","book":"Act","chapter":11,"verse":25,"letter":"d"},{"kind":"text","text":" "}],"crossRefs":[{"label":"Nm 23:7","book":"Num","chapter":23,"verse":7},{"label":"Lk 2:2","book":"Luk","chapter":2,"verse":2},{"label":"Ac 9:30","book":"Act","chapter":9,"verse":30},{"label":"Ac 11:25–26","book":"Act","chapter":11,"verse":25}],"footnotes":[]},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Gal:1:22","parts":[{"kind":"text","text":"I remained personally unknown to the Judean churches that are in Christ. "}],"crossRefs":[],"footnotes":[]},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Gal:1:23","parts":[{"kind":"text","text":"They simply kept hearing, “He who formerly persecuted "},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Ac 8:1–3","book":"Act","chapter":8,"verse":1,"letter":"a"},{"kind":"text","text":" us now preaches the faith "},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Jd 1:3","book":"Jud","chapter":1,"verse":3,"letter":"b"},{"kind":"text","text":" he once tried to destroy.” "}],"crossRefs":[{"label":"Ac 8:1–3","book":"Act","chapter":8,"verse":1},{"label":"Jd 1:3","book":"Jud","chapter":1,"verse":3}],"footnotes":[]},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Gal:1:24","parts":[{"kind":"text","text":"And they glorified God because of me. "},{"kind":"footnote","marker":1,"text":"Or in me"}],"crossRefs":[],"footnotes":[{"marker":1,"text":"Or in me"}]}]},"cachedAt":1783099544527}